  "original_title": "\u0dc3\u0dbb\u0dca\u0dc0 \u0db4\u0dcf\u0d9a\u0dca\u0dc2\u0dd2\u0d9a \u0d86\u0dab\u0dca\u0da9\u0dd4\u0dc0\u0d9a\u0da7 \u0dc3\u0dc4\u0dcf\u0dba \u0daf\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dca\u0db1 \u0dc1\u0dca\u200d\u0dbb\u0dd3\u0dbd\u0db1\u0dd2\u0db4\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dca \u0d9a\u0ddc\u0db1\u0dca\u0daf\u0dda\u0dc3\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Sri Lankan conditions to support an all-party government",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Mr. Yasiri Jayasekara, General Secretary of the Sri Lanka Freedom Party said in Kandy that the Sri Lanka Freedom Party has full support for an all-party government, but the cabinet appointed for it should be a small number of people and there should be no allegations of corruption.",
        "He said this yesterday morning (13) while speaking to the media after coming to Sri Dalada Palace and paying obeisance to Lord Dalada.",
        "\"Political stability is very important to stabilize the country economically. For that, full support is given to an all-party government, but no request for ministership has been made so far.",
        "The government has prepared plans to reduce the losses of the government institutions which have been making losses for many years instead of burdening the public.",
        "Electricity Board, Ceylon Petroleum Statutory Corporation, Water Supply and Drainage Board etc. have been increasing the salaries of the employees once in three years due to a situation where they are making losses.",
        "It is important for the economic development of this country to establish a national council and prepare an economic program consisting of all party leaders."
      ],
